title: The Lone Ranger S01E03-E04
description:
The Lone Ranger

The Sole Survivor of a posse of Texas Rangers ambushed by a gang of desperados, John Reid was left for dead and nursed back to health by Tonto (Jay Silverheels), a friendly Indian whom he had once helped. With a black mask and silver bullets from the mine he discovered with his brother, one of the slain Rangers, Reid sets out astride his horse, Silver, to right the wrongs of the West as The Lone Ranger (Clayton Moore)

Episode 03 The Lone Ranger's Triumph

In the conclusion of his three-part origin, "The Lone Ranger's Triumph", he saves Sheriff "Two-Gun" Taylor (Walter Sande), the kidnapped Doc Drummond (George Chesebro), and the tow of Colby from Cavendish. Then,

Episode 04 Legion of Old Timers

Red Devers (Norman Willis) tries to steal the Circle K Ranch from Bob Kittredge (Star Trek's Deforest Kelley), until the disguised Ranger and foreman Banty Bishop (Emmett Lynn) form a "Legion of Old Timers".

Approximately 48 Minutes
Converted from VHS
